        Unlike traditional module federation, 1fe's dynamic runtime orchestrates micro-frontends through live configs. Change widget versions, update features, or rollback instantlyâ€”all without touching your main app.
      </p>

      <ul class="grid mt-6 text-left gap-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-neutral-800">
          <Icon name="ph:check-circle-fill" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" aria-hidden="true" />
